---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Docs">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner docs">
      <p class="eyebrow">Docs</p>
      <h1>Trading reference</h1>
      <p class="lead">A concise guide to using My MetaTrader: wallets, leverage, risk, and yield vaults.</p>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Getting started</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Install MetaMask or any EVM-compatible wallet and fund it with the asset you want to trade.</li>
          <li>Connect your wallet to My MetaTrader and approve the DEX contract for the trading pair.</li>
          <li>Select a pair, choose your leverage ratio, and always set a stop-loss before confirming.</li>
          <li>Review position size, margin requirements, and liquidation price before executing any trade.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Risk checklist</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>High leverage amplifies both gains and losses. Never risk more than you can afford to lose.</li>
          <li>Use stop-loss orders on every trade. Unprotected positions can be liquidated quickly.</li>
          <li>Monitor margin health. Add margin or reduce position size if approaching liquidation.</li>
          <li>Understand funding rates and fees. These accrue while positions remain open.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Yield vaults</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Deposit stablecoins into vaults to earn real yield from protocol trading fees.</li>
          <li>Yield is paid in kind. There are no inflationary token emissions.</li>
          <li>Deposits and withdrawals are on-chain and non-custodial.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs {
    display: grid;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 22px;
    color: #354052;
  }

  pre {
    overflow: auto;
    margin: 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #111827;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 18px;
  }
</style>
